很久很久沒有更新了！<br />只想跟大家說，我過得很好，有點忙過頭了！<br />目前人在加州，很努力的過生活。<br />這是幾個月前根據"文具盒女孩"一文所畫出的繪本，拿去當做研究所申請的備審材料之一。<br />心情不好的時候，我就會回頭看一看，提醒自己我是誰 :)<br /><br />希望大家喜歡這個小故事。<br /><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-NnkHgSEDE64/UO1u04a2b0I/AAAAAAAAA4k/hpifFkCuo5c/s1600/1cover.png" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-NnkHgSEDE64/UO1u04a2b0I/AAAAAAAAA4k/hpifFkCuo5c/s1600/1cover.png" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-hriA02GqLdU/UO1vxghclRI/AAAAAAAAA50/8b0BbYBKtB4/s1600/preface.png" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-hriA02GqLdU/UO1vxghclRI/AAAAAAAAA50/8b0BbYBKtB4/s1600/preface.png" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-wTqUEpky7Uw/UO1x3BjfJCI/AAAAAAAAA7g/bfjWPwDidyE/s1600/1story.png" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-wTqUEpky7Uw/UO1x3BjfJCI/AAAAAAAAA7g/bfjWPwDidyE/s1600/1story.png" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><br /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-7kKuGyT_4dc/UO1u3NPGhwI/AAAAAAAAA4s/Z6U6LMMud18/s1600/2.png" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-7kKuGyT_4dc/UO1u3NPGhwI/AAAAAAAAA4s/Z6U6LMMud18/s1600/2.png" /></a></div><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-9eRNJ1Ztg1U/UO1vOqDafiI/AAAAAAAAA5U/DtfptR06DD0/s1600/3.png" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-9eRNJ1Ztg1U/UO1vOqDafiI/AAAAAAAAA5U/DtfptR06DD0/s1600/3.png" /></a></div><br /><d